{"tid":2491634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府晤業界 不宜打針者可擇名申報則獲放寬 正研發新的「打針好市民」系統","createTime":"2021-04-16T12:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:51:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b159801b059a134317c3ddc1b464c31aa45bc7e3","tid":2491634,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"黃家和：當局讓不宜接種疫苗餐飲業員工申報後毋須打針<br />\n<br />\n政府就有關「疫苗氣泡」安排約見飲食及酒吧業界代表。香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和會後表示，政府正設計一份申報表，讓一些身體狀況不宜接種疫苗，或有特殊情況的員工填寫後，可以毋須接種疫苗，所屬餐飲處所都能享有「疫苗氣泡」下的放寬社交距離安排。<br />\n<br />\n黃家和又透露，政府正設計一個新應用程式，證明程式使用者已接種疫苗，方便食肆執行「疫苗氣泡」安排。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387574&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=1b3ba084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387574</a>"},{"pid":"48d2c4c3e5720a6647aaba1a2fcc390ae0630a76","tid":2491634,"uid":55633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b159801b059a134317c3ddc1b464c31aa45bc7e3","tid":2491634,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"黃家和：當局讓不宜接種疫苗餐飲業員工申報後毋須打針<br />\n<br />\n政府就有關「疫苗氣泡」安排約見飲食及酒吧業界代表。香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和會後表示，政府正設計一份申報表，讓一些身體狀況不宜接種疫苗，或有特殊情況的員工填寫後，可以毋須接種疫苗，所屬餐飲處所都能享有「疫苗氣泡」下的放寬社交距離安排。<br />\n<br />\n黃家和又透露，政府正設計一個新應用程式，證明程式使用者已接種疫苗，方便食肆執行「疫苗氣泡」安排。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387574&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=1b3ba084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387574</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks."},{"pid":"f6cac097d80cf9adb696fdd188aad3b42afa8024","tid":2491634,"uid":240004,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔打針就扣社會信用評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0207e0746562484c3b71f39a6245338e5318494","tid":2491634,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"此外，新疆街上更設有具備人面辨識功能的監控鏡頭，以及廣泛設置檢查站。《獨立報》亦引述人權組識指，當局利用人工智能及大數據技術，分析每個居民，將他們分為「放心戶」、「一般戶」、「不放心戶」 3 大類別，並進行不同度監視及管制。而中國政府更會收集當地居民的 DNA、指紋、虹膜、血型、聲紋、頭部的 360 度影像等，對居民造成極大壓力。"},{"pid":"9ddbc22fe9a7d8edaf29a6fb38bdec0b4a533d6e","tid":2491634,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"打針好巿民 名都柒過人"},{"pid":"1d0987eb553d8f30bf185cb694dd78eb7e329c76","tid":2491634,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"成個大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae2f7897d134aeaec5acdd108d2745346ada36a","tid":2491634,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"禁足者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a581e87b843af6800d61664f0ef45c9f0608d279","tid":2491634,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b3543b1922fe6e2322a05b3c843c8e821169dd","tid":2491634,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6cac097d80cf9adb696fdd188aad3b42afa8024","tid":2491634,"uid":240004,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔打針就扣社會信用評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"用社會信用評級迫你打"},{"pid":"d72288dba9b44cfc00d1040a09b383e97705377c","tid":2491634,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"支那好聲音d friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c